      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. that sounds like a good start for the vibe we want. you mentioned maintaining a neutral expression to avoid looking \"unrefined\"... can you expand on that? like, if a client travels to regions like East Asia or West Africa, what specific non-Western behaviors or styles should they specifically avoid if they want to stay within that \"sophisticated\" global standard?",
